text: —You desire to correct a statement which you made in your evidence ?
—I wish to explain that it was the polling-booth I meant that the candidates went into.
4047. You wish to substitute the word - polling-booth' for what other word ?
—You know John M'Swan who was examined here
4049. The property he is on is the property of Glendale ?
4050. It has nothing to do with the M'Leod property ?
